Introduction

HINT was a South Korean girl group formed by Star Pro Entertainment. Originally debuting as TURAN, they changed their name to HINT in mid 2017 and debuted with a new line up under Swan Media Entertainment.

The members announced on Instagram that HINT has disbanded as of September 27, 2022.
